00:00:37,750 --> 00:00:38,940
我要去买炸鸡，你要不要？
Want some chicken?

8
00:00:39,050 --> 00:00:40,850
不了，谢谢，再见
No,thanks. No chicken. Bye-bye.

9
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:45,660
你确定？有额外的脆脆的大米哦？
You sure? Some extra-crispy,dirty rice?

10
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:48,450
我最后一次说我不要了 出去，乔伊
For the last time,no! Get out,Joey!

11
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,790
知道了
All right.

12
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:58,200
你没事吧？抱歉，他死都不走 缠着我问要不要炸鸡
Are you okay? I'm so sorry!He wouldn't leave.He kept asking me if I wanted chicken.

13
00:00:58,870 --> 00:01:00,460
炸鸡？
Chicken?

14
00:01:01,270 --> 00:01:02,800
我想吃炸鸡
I could eat some chicken.

15
00:01:04,580 --> 00:01:05,910
乔伊
Hey Joey

16
00:01:08,350 --> 00:01:13,510
我要三块鸡、沙拉 豆子、可乐
Could I get a three-piece,some coleslaw,some beans and a Coke?

17
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,880
