早安
-Morning,

26
00:01:58,730 --> 00:01:59,590
早安，菲比
Phoebe.

27
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:01,860
我非告诉你们不可
-I have to tell you this story.

28
00:02:01,970 --> 00:02:04,260
刚才载我来的司机…
I was coming over and this cabdriver

29
00:02:04,370 --> 00:02:06,170
那人是不是叫做安格斯？
Was his name Angus?

30
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:08,170
什么？
What?

31
00:02:08,270 --> 00:02:10,330
我们在伦敦碰到的计程车司机
He was a cabdriver we had in London.

32
00:02:12,810 --> 00:02:14,840
好吧，总之…
All right. Anyway

33
00:02:14,950 --> 00:02:17,140
他载我们去的酒馆叫什么？
What was that pub he took us to?

34
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:17,870
麦子酒馆
The Wheat Sheaf!

35
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:20,210
对，那里有一种啤酒…
And they had that beer....

36
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,010
柏丁顿
Boddington's!

37
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:23,140
就是柏丁顿
Boddington's!

38
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,710
菲比有话要说
Phoebe was going to tell a story.

39
00:02:28,530 --> 00:02:31,980
他的帽子很好笑… 我不想说了
So he had a really funny hat.I don't want to talk about it.

40
00:02:35,370 --> 00:02:37,770
罗斯，柏丁顿
-Hey. -Hey,Ross!Boddington's!

41
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:39,300
是啊
Oh,man!

42
00:02:42,570 --> 00:02:46,370
若是能再喝一杯 要我走回伦敦都行
I'd walk back to London for another frosty one of those bad boys.

43
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:49,140
世贸附近的英国酒馆好像有
They have them at the British pub by the Trade Center.

44
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:50,210
回头见
Later!

45
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,470
瑞秋不是应该回来了吗？
Shouldn't Rachel be back?

46
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:55,280
可是班机在雅典误点
Her plane got delayed.

47
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:56,980
不过现在也该到了
But she should be here by now.

48
00:02:57,090 --> 00:03:00,350
你跟她通过电话 她很生气吗？
So you talked to her? Did she sound mad?

49
00:03:00,460 --> 00:03:02,390
不会，那是因为她喜欢我
No. But she likes me.

50
00:03:03,530 --> 00:03:04,960
你丢下她让她独自飞到希腊去
You abandoned her on a plane to Greece.

51
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:08,620
我才没有丢下瑞秋
I did not "abandon" Rachel. Okay?

52
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:11,700
艾蜜莉出现在机场 我当然得去追她
Emily showed up at the airport.I had to go after her. 

53
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:16,740
我别无选择 毕竟她是我妻子，瑞秋是我妻子
I did what I had to do.She's my wife. Rachel is my wife.

54
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,310
是…艾蜜莉
Emily!

55
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:24,910
艾蜜莉是我老婆 我是怎么了？
Emily is my wife.Man,what is that?

56
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:28,120
你还没有艾蜜莉的消息？
You haven't heard from Emily?

57
00:03:28,220 --> 00:03:30,690
我在机场追丢之后就没有了
Not since I lost her at the airport.

58
00:03:30,790 --> 00:03:32,760
她竟然跑得比你快
I can't believe she can outrun you.

59
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:35,830
她是很快，好吗？
Hey! She's fast,okay?

60
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:39,390
你自以为能快过我？ 我们现在就去外头较量
You think you can beat me? Let's go! Outside!

61
00:03:41,970 --> 00:03:43,990
抱歉，我太…
-I'm sorry. I'm just a little

62
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:44,930
慢了？
-Slow?

63
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,900
你要跟我比比吗？
Oh,you want some?!

64
00:03:47,010 --> 00:03:49,870
走啊，去穿球鞋，我们去赛跑
Okay,get the shoes on! Let's go,man!

65
00:03:50,610 --> 00:03:53,670
别激动，你跑得最快
It's cool,okay?You're the fastest!

66
00:03:55,810 --> 00:03:57,110
嗨
-Hi! 

67
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,650
瑞秋 嗨
-Oh,my God,Rachel!

68
00:03:59,550 --> 00:04:01,580
瑞秋，我很抱歉
Rach,I am so sorry.

69
00:04:01,690 --> 00:04:04,150
非常对不起你
 I am so,so sorry.

70
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:07,090
罗斯，你没做错
Come on. You just did what you had to do.

71
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:09,160
嗨，菲比
Hi，Phoebe

72
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:11,160
就这样？你不生气？
That's it? You're not mad?

73
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:12,920
你应该很火大
 It must've been terrible.

74
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:16,330
火大？我可是在希腊
Terrible? Hell,I was in Greece!

75
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:20,430
那间饭店非常棒 海滩很美，人又和善
There was a nice hotel,nice beach,met the nice people.

76
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:22,370
对我瑞秋来说可不差
It's not too shabby for Rachel.

77
00:04:25,610 --> 00:04:28,200
就这样？不生气？
So,what,that's it?

78
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:32,410
对，我没生你的气
We're cool. Totally cool.

79
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:34,610
谢谢，你真好
Thanks,Rach. You're the best.

80
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,520
你才好呢
Oh,no. You're the best.

81
00:04:38,590 --> 00:04:40,390
我要去花店一趟
Oh,I got to go to the flower store.

82
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:44,460
听我说，大家都不肯说 艾蜜莉在哪里
No one will tell me where Emily is...

83
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:48,900
我决定买72朵长茎红玫瑰 送去艾蜜莉爸妈家
...so I'm sending 72 long-stemmed,red roses to her parents' house.

84
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,990
每朵代表我认识她 并且深爱她的每一天
One for each day I've known and loved her.

85
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:53,800
她一定会感动地软化
That should get her talking.

86
00:04:53,910 --> 00:04:57,710
罗斯，写卡片时别忘了 对方是“艾蜜莉”
When you make out the card,be sure to make it out to "Emily."

87
00:05:02,980 --> 00:05:06,110
瑞秋，太好了 幸好你在希腊玩得开心
It's good that you had such a good time in Greece.

88
00:05:07,050 --> 00:05:08,520
什么？
What?

89
00:05:09,790 --> 00:05:12,690
我在希腊才不开心
I didn't have a good time in Greece!

90
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:15,450
罗斯丢下我一人
Ross abandoned me!

91
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:19,620
我买不到机票回来 只好住在他们的蜜月套房
I couldn't get a plane out. I had to stay in their suite!

92
00:05:19,730 --> 00:05:21,460
每个人都要来问我
People came up to me going,

93
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:24,260
“盖勒太太，你哭什么？”
"Mrs. Geller! Why are you cry?"

94
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:30,870
简直丢死人了，我真是个白痴
I mean,it was so humiliating!I felt like such an idiot!

95
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:32,310
这都是我的错
It's all my fault. 

96
00:05:32,410 --> 00:05:36,850
你们知道为什么吗？ 因为我的决定都不对
You know why?Because I make very bad decisions.

97
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:37,920
不要这么说
Oh,that's not true.

98
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:42,010
就是这样，我没胡说 我跑去蠢伦敦追罗斯
Yes,it is true. I went after Ross in stupid London!

99
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,550
伦敦的确是个蠢地方！太蠢了
London is stupid! Stupid!

100
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:49,730
打扮得像个啦啦队长 倒追约书亚
I put on a cheerleading outfit to seduce Joshua.

101
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:54,460
约了四次会就叫他娶我 把他吓死了
Then I lost him because I asked him to marry me after four dates.

102
00:05:54,570 --> 00:05:59,060
然后我还去希腊渡别人的蜜月
And then I went to Greece on somebody else's honeymoon. Okay?

103
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:02,440
你们觉得这些决定正确吗？
Do those sound like very good decisions to you?

104
00:06:02,910 --> 00:06:04,740
我喜欢你的小辫子
I like your little braid.

105
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:08,140
我不应该做任何决定
I just shouldn't be allowed to make decisions anymore.

106
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:11,010
菲比，你说得对 我根本不该去伦敦
Phoebe,you were right. I should've never gone to London.

107
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:15,210
从现在开始由你帮我做决定
From now on,you make all my decisions for me.

108
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,310
不行，我以前就这么做过
Oh,no. I did that for someone once.

109
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:21,380
我不喜欢主宰别人的生活
I'm not comfortable having that power over someone's life.

110
00:06:21,490 --> 00:06:22,890
那我来
I'll do it.

111
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:27,960
很好，莫妮卡 以后由你主宰我的感情生活
Fine. Monica,you are now in charge of my love life.

112
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:30,490
我该去上班了
Okay. I got to go to work.

113
00:06:41,810 --> 00:06:44,010
瑞秋，很高兴看到你回来
And Rachel,great to have you back.

114
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:49,780
菲比
Phoebe

115
00:06:55,890 --> 00:06:57,330
真开心
Always a pleasure.

116
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,140
瑞秋，亲爱的，你看
Rachel? Sweetie,look.

117
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:11,040
这是你跟乔伊在招待会的照片
Here's a cute picture of you and Joey.

118
00:07:11,140 --> 00:07:12,440
他已经结婚了
He's married.

119
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:15,070
罗斯结婚了 我到现在还不敢相信
Ross is married. I still can't believe it.

120
00:07:16,210 --> 00:07:17,880
亲爱的，抓旁边就好
Honey,sweetie,by the edges.

121
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:20,840
看来我只好接受事实
I'll just have to accept it.

122
00:07:20,950 --> 00:07:22,780
这都要怪我
I mean,it's my fault.

123
00:07:23,290 --> 00:07:25,590
别抓中间，指纹会弄脏照片
Edges! Fingers! Smudgy!

124
00:07:25,690 --> 00:07:26,750
天啊
Oh,my God!

125
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:34,350
算了
That's okay.

126
00:07:34,470 --> 00:07:37,530
我知道你心情低落 不是故意找我麻烦
 I know that you're very upset right now.I know that wasn't about me.

127
00:07:37,970 --> 00:07:39,490
我看她就是跟她作对
I bet it was about her a little.

128
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:44,240
你要是肯放下罗斯一分钟 就会发现到处有帅哥
If you'd stop thinking about Ross...you'd notice there are great guys everywhere.

129
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:47,800
你看，例如甘瑟
Look. Gunther.

130
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:51,840
他既善良又可爱
He's nice. He's cute.

131
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,480
甘瑟的确…
Yeah. I guess Gunther is....

132
00:07:54,590 --> 00:07:56,350
还有那边那个家伙
What about that guy over there?

133
00:07:57,660 --> 00:08:00,820
记得吗？你以前 跟他打情骂俏过
That's the guy you flirted with at the counter.

134
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,730
我不知道…
-Oh,I don't know. I don't know.

135
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,160
你现在就去跟他说话
-You're going to talk to him.

136
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:09,320
我们说好由我发号施令 我命令你去跟他说话
I make your decisions,and I say you're going to talk to him.

137
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,230
好吧，你说了算
All right.You're the boss. 

138
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:14,500
看来我只好照办
I got to do what you tell me.

139
00:08:14,610 --> 00:08:16,400
他听到这句话肯定上钩
Say that to him,and you're golden.

140
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:24,140
菲比
Hey,Phoebe.

141
00:08:24,250 --> 00:08:25,840
伦敦的照片洗出来了
 We got our pictures back from London.

142
00:08:25,950 --> 00:08:28,350
这张是所有人在伦敦塔拍的
Here's all of us at the Tower of London....

143
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:30,920
大家都在照片中
Here we all are.

144
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,850
有罗斯、乔伊、你…
There's Ross and Joey and you and

145
00:08:35,230 --> 00:08:37,250
和我
And me.

146
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,820
你一定听烦我们说伦敦的事了
We've been talking about London too much.

147
00:08:40,930 --> 00:08:43,900
是我不好，因为我去不了
Sorry,it's just because I couldn't be there.

148
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:47,560
我只能大着肚子 烦都快烦死了
All I get to do now is pregnant stuff. It bums me out.

149
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:50,370
很抱歉…
-I'm sorry. -Sorry.

150
00:08:50,470 --> 00:08:52,670
你知道我伤心时都怎么做吗？
Know what I like to do? 

151
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:54,140
有时候事情不太顺利
It sounds a little corny...but sometimes when I'm bummed out,

152
00:08:54,250 --> 00:08:59,240
我就闭上眼睛 想想人生实在挺美好
I like to just close my eyes...and think about what a wonderful gift life is.

153
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,690
有用吧？
See?

154
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:12,130
怎么样？
-What happened? 

155
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:14,460
总之我们东扯西扯
-A little of this,a little of that.

156
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:16,360
明天晚上要出去约会
I got myself a date tomorrow.

157
00:09:16,470 --> 00:09:20,430
看吧？你就要忘记罗斯了
See? Didn't I tell you? You're getting over Ross already.

158
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:25,540
滚出去 “我们有权利拒绝服务”
Get out.

159
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:40,160
你怎么去那么久？
What took so long?

160
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:41,420
公事担搁了
I got caught up at work. 

161
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:44,090
不过我明天就辞职
But I'm quitting tomorrow.

162
00:09:48,730 --> 00:09:50,290
谢谢你邀我过来
So thanks for having me over.

163
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,700
瑞秋
Rachel

164
00:09:59,980 --> 00:10:01,170
菲比
Phoebe

165
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:10,250
再见
See you,man.

166
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,020
他发什么神经？
What the hell was that?

167
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:19,590
可能在伦敦学到的欧洲风俗
Probably some European goodbye thing he picked up in London.

168
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,660
那才不是欧洲风俗
That's not European.

169
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:24,030
比较像法式热吻
It felt French.

170
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:30,500
换我跟各位老友说再见了
Well,I guess it's time for me to say goodbye too,mon frere.

171
00:10:32,380 --> 00:10:33,840
过来给我点甜头吧
Come here and give me a little sugar.

172
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:43,480
我玩得好开心
I really had a good time.

173
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:44,850
我也是
Yeah,me too.

174
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:49,250
看来今天要结束了
I guess this is it.

175
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:54,660
除非你想进来 好
Unless you want to come inside? Yeah

176
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:59,700
等等，我无法自做主张
Wait a minute. You know what? I can't decide this.

177
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:05,270
等我一下 好
Okay. Just hold on a second.

178
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:13,610
莫妮卡在吗？我有事要问她
Where's Monica? I have to ask her something.

179
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,650
她去洗衣服
Doing her laundry.

